ry]]}}\n| extra14  = [[Brian Rawling]]\n| length14 = 3:44\n\n| total_length = 49:36\n}}\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed = yes\n| headline = Digital / Vinyl Bonus Tracks\n| extra_column = Producer(s)\n\n| title15   = Dear Santa\n| writer15  = {{hlist|Gingell|Stone|[[Una Healy]]}}\n| extra15   = The Alias\n| length15  = 3:03\n\n| title16   = Scared of the Dark\n| note16    = Acoustic\n| writer16  = {{hlist|Ryden|Bevan}}\n| extra16   = {{hlist|The Alias|Ryden}}\n| length16  = 4:01\n\n| title17   = Dancing With a Broken Heart \n| note17    = 7th Heaven Radio Mix\n| writer17  = {{hlist|Goodrem|Pizzinga|Shanks}}\n| extra17   = {{hlist|The Alias|7th Heaven}}\n| length17  = 3:29\n\n| title18   = Story of a Heart\n| note18    = 7th Heaven Radio Mix\n| writer18  = {{hlist|Andersson|Ulvaeus}}\n| extra18   = {{hlist|The Alias|7th Heaven}}\n| length18  = 3:33\n\n| title19   = Neon Blue\n| note19    = Adam Turner Radio Edit\n| writer19  = {{hlist|Ryden|Bevan}}\n| extra19   = {{hlist|The Alias|Ryden|Adam Turner}}\n| length19  = 4:05\n\n| title20   = Scared of the Dark\n| note20    = 7th Heaven Radio Mix\n| writer20  = {{hlist|Ryden|Bevan}}\n| extra20   = {{hlist|The Alias|Ryden|7th Heaven}}\n| length20  = 4:24\n\n| title21   = Happy\n| note21    = Club Junkies Radio Mix\n| writer21  = {{hlist|Mac|Wroldsen}}\n| extra21   = {{hlist|The Alias|Club Junkies}}\n| length21  = 3:37\n\n| title22   = Glitter & Gold\n| note22    = Rescue Rangerz Radio Mix\n| writer22  = {{hlist|Stone|Gingell}}\n| extra22   = {{hlist|The Alias|Rescue Rangerz}}\n| length22  = 4:00\n\n| title23  = I Will Love Again\n| note23   = Porl Young Radio Mix\n| writer23 = {{hlist|Taylor|Barry}}\n| extra23  = {{hlist|Rawling|Porl Young}}\n| length23 = 3:57\n\n| title24   = Tears on the Dancefloor\n| note24    = DJ David Strong 7th Heaven Medley\n| writer24  = {{hlist|Falk|Hayes}}\n| extra24   = {{hlist|The Alias|DJ David|7th Heaven}}\n| length24  = 7:19\n\n| total_length = 93:55\n}}\n\n'''Notes'''\n*\"Dancing with a Broken Heart\" is a cover of the song originally performed by [[Delta Goodrem]].\n*\"You Make Me Whole\" is a cover of the song originally performed by Zoe Zana<ref>{{Citation|title=You Make Me Whole|url=https://soundcloud.com/zoe-zana/you-make-me-whole|language=en|accessdate=2017-09-22}}</ref>  and later by [[Aneta Sablik]] & [[Anna Naklab]].\n*\"Story of a Heart\" is a cover of the song originally performed by [[Benny Anderssons orkester|Benny Andersson's solo band]].\n*\"No More Tears on the Dancefloor\" is a cover of the [[Thomas Anders|Anders]]|[[J\u00f6rn-Uwe Fahrenkrog-Petersen|Fahrenkrog]] song.<!-- \"Anders|Fahrenkrog\" That is how it is spelled. With the | between the names.  -->\n*\"I Will Love Again\" is a cover of the song originally performed by [[Lara Fabian]].\n*\"Tears on the Dancefloor\" is a medley of the 7th Heaven Remixes of \"Scared of the Dark\", \"Story of a Heart\", \"Neon Blue\" and \"Dancing with a Broken Heart\".\n\n===Charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2017)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br>position\n|-\n{{album chart|Scotland|6|date=2017-11-09|rowheader=true|accessdate=29 November 2017}}\n|-\n{{album chart|UK|6|date=2017-11-09|rowheader=true|accessdate=29 November 2017}}\n|-\n{{album chart|UKIndependent|1|date=2017-11-09|rowheader=true|accessdate=29 November 2017}}\n|}\n\n==Release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|+ List of release dates, showing country, format, label and references\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Country\n! scope=\"col\" | Date\n! scope=\"col\" | Format\n! scope=\"col\" | Label\n! scope=\"col\" | {{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\" | United Kingdom\n| rowspan=\"5\"| 21 April 2017\n| [[Music download|Digital download]]\n| rowspan=\"6\"| Steps Music LLP\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"UK Download Track listing Official Store\">{{cite web|url=https://store.stepsofficial.co.uk/products/tears-on-the-dancefloo